Dapper currently doesn&#39;t have a count of the available resultsets in the `GridReader`.

But you can use the `IsConsumed` property instead, once all resultsets are processed, `IsConsumed` is set to `false`. 

```csharp
while (!result.IsConsumed)
{
   dynamic rs = result.Read();
}
```

